(121, 3, '2009-07-01 12:24:20', '2009-07-01 12:24:20', 'Curt W. Pletcher works with schools, cities, towns, counties and  libraries, providing financial advisory services for financing and  refinancing opportunities as well as providing other client accounting  and financial services. Pletcher has more than 25 years of financial and  accounting management experience in the public and private sectors.\r\n\r\nPletcher, a graduate of Indiana University, joined Umbaugh  in 2000.  He is a member of the Indiana CPA Society and the American  Institute of Certified Public Accountants. He also serves as a member of  the John Glenn School Corporation Board of Trustees.', 'Curt W. Pletcher', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'curt-w-pletcher', '', '', '2011-01-25 16:06:26', '2011-01-25 16:06:26', '', 0, 'http://localhost/umbaugh/?post_type=partner&p=121', 0, 'partner', '', 0),
