(250, 1, '2011-01-17 23:50:39', '2011-01-17 23:50:39', '<h2><a href="http://markup.umbaugh.com/login/#">Bid UMBAUGH</a></h2>\r\nTo better serve the needs of our clients issuing  bonds through a competitive bidding process, we have partnered with  Grant Street Group to offer electronic bidding services. Electronic  bidding provides our clients with better access to the municipal bond  market, creating interest from investment bankers from across the  nation. Access to the national bond markets frequently increases the  number bids received for bonds being issued competitively, and can  result in lower interest costs for the bonds.\r\n<h2><a href="http://markup.umbaugh.com/login/#">Employee Portal</a></h2>\r\nUmbaugh Employee Links. This site is restricted to Umbaugh employees.\r\n<h2><a href="http://markup.umbaugh.com/login/#">Upload Stuff!</a></h2>\r\n<form enctype="multipart/form-data" method="POST">\r\n<blockquote><input name="dest" type="hidden" />\r\n<table><tr><td><input style="width: 460px; border-top: 1px solid #aaa; border-left: 1px solid #aaa; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; border-right: 1px solid #eee;" name="file" size="70" type="file" />\r\n</td></tr><tr><td>\r\n<input style="width: 460px; border-top: 1px solid #aaa; border-left: 1px solid #aaa; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; border-right: 1px solid #eee;" name="email" size="70" type="text" value="Email"/> \r\n</td></tr><tr><td>\r\n<textarea style="width: 460px; border-top: 1px solid #aaa; border-left: 1px solid #aaa; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; border-right: 1px solid #eee;" name="comments" cols="100" rows="3">Comments</textarea> <br>\r\n<input style="padding: 4px; width: 100px; background-color: #cccccc; border: 1px solid #555555; color: #000;" type="submit" value="Upload" />\r\n</td></tr></table></blockquote>\r\n</form>', 'Login', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '53-autosave', '', '', '2011-01-17 23:50:39', '2011-01-17 23:50:39', '', 53, 'http://localhost/umbaugh/53-autosave', 0, 'revision', '