(545, 3, '2009-05-27 20:09:32', '2009-05-27 20:09:32', 'Redevelopment Commissions have until July 15 to determine whether their TIF areas have excess TIF revenue.  To do this, you will need to compare the amount of TIF being captured to the amount you will need to pay for debt service and other identified needs in the coming year.  This is the second year for the July 15 deadline for TIF analysis.\r\n\r\n<em>If you need help computing TIF requirements and whether it is advantageous to pass through excess TIF collections, please contact us.</em>', 'Reminder - July 15 is the Deadline for TIF Analysis', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'reminder-july-15-is-the-deadline-for-tif-analysis', '', '', '2011-01-25 15:40:42', '2011-01-25 15:40:42', '', 0, 'http://dev.umbaugh.com/?p=545', 0, 'post', '', 0),
