ssed value</strong> rather than its population or the cost of providing services to the annexed area.</p>\n\n<p><em>Umbaugh can help your municipality estimate the additional revenue potential for an annexation as well as the cost of providing services. If you have questions or need assistance, please contact us.</em></p>', 'Municipal Annexation: Will It Generate the Revenue You Expect?', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'open', '', '572-revision', '', '', '2011-01-18 21:56:54', '2011-01-18 21:56:54', '', 572, 'http://dev.umbaugh.com/572-revision', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
